OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny patchy mist of fog first
OL,6,Fthing will quickly clear. Then it will
OL,7,Fbe a dry day with warm sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping between patchy amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and bright evening with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. The rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will see clear spells, and
OL,14,Fperhaps the odd mist or fog patch
OL,15,Fdeveloping later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FDry and bright with the
OL,18,Fbest chance of some bright or hazy
OL,19,Fsunny spells during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
