OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly dry with very warm sunshine on
OL,7,FWednesday and Thursday. Cloudier later
OL,8,FThursday and Friday morning with the
OL,9,Frisk of a few showers.
